        <hl1>QUOTATION OF THE DAY</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>''Despite all my family's suffering, I think that this has allowed me to meet very beautiful and brilliant people in this country. And I hope in the future, this same impression I took from this country can become true between Cuba and the United States.''</p>
        <p>JUAN MIGUEL GONZALEZ, before boarding a plane to Cuba with his son, Elian. [A14]</p>
      </block>
